Package com.charliai.activities.api

Class ActivityConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.charliai.activities.api.ActivityConfig
  • public class ActivityConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    The ActivityConfig class defines the configuration of the activity handler and will initialize the activity handler. This class will also register the activity handler with the registry and provide access to the configuration. The ActivityConfig is only set based on the configuration and runtime values.
    Author:
    kevincollins

        public ActivityConfig​(org.json.JSONObject activity)
